title.narrative: Pakistan - Trade Related Technical Assistance (TRTA II) Programme

description.narrative: The overarching goal of this extension is to address issues of economic growth and employment creation. The goal stems directly from the current needs of the country and is also in line with the broader EU cooperation strategy. This addendum to the original cooperation agreement now incorporates the structure of this extension programme. This extended period will be spent to complete few of the lagged activities to deepen some of the successes of TRTA II to bring them to a logical conclusion and to develop a strategy for EU intervention beyond this period.
